259
00:12:11,264 --> 00:12:12,632
Is that so?

260
00:12:12,699 --> 00:12:14,334
-I'm excited.
-Well…

261
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,336
-Japanese people…
-Yes?

262
00:12:16,402 --> 00:12:20,139
They probably wouldn't even imagine
drinking the broth.

263
00:12:20,273 --> 00:12:21,908
Well, it's good broth…

264
00:12:21,975 --> 00:12:24,110
-Broth…
-Of course, there's a bit of seasoning.

265
00:12:24,244 --> 00:12:27,013
-But it's not all artificial.
