355
00:17:43,296 --> 00:17:45,364
But if you do it from the beginning…

356
00:17:45,431 --> 00:17:46,966
-It makes it murky?
-Yes.

357
00:17:47,033 --> 00:17:48,167
-Right.
-Yes.

358
00:17:58,678 --> 00:18:02,582
This is top-tier,
