359
00:18:02,648 --> 00:18:04,584
-I'm glad you like it.
-Yes.

360
00:18:06,886 --> 00:18:08,988
Can I add some vinegar?

361
00:18:09,055 --> 00:18:11,390
-No.
-No? I can't?

362
00:18:11,457 --> 00:18:12,758
-Of course you can.
-Yes.

363
00:18:12,825 --> 00:18:13,893
-I can?
-Go ahead.

364
00:18:15,628 --> 00:18:17,029
-It's your preference.
-Yes.

365
00:18:18,297 --> 00:18:19,632
I want to change the flavor.

366
00:18:21,233 --> 00:18:22,368
Oh…

367
00:18:25,304 --> 00:18:26,706
-Nice.
