413
00:20:29,929 --> 00:20:30,996
Oh…

414
00:20:31,097 --> 00:20:33,399
-No toppings.
-I see.

415
00:20:33,466 --> 00:20:36,168
-They give you noodles…
-Yes.

416
00:20:36,235 --> 00:20:38,704
-…without meat or eggs.
-Oh…

417
00:20:52,818 --> 00:20:54,720
The broth is getting better by the minute.

418
00:20:54,787 --> 00:20:55,955
-Really?
-Yes.

419
00:21:00,059 --> 00:21:01,060
It's here.

420
00:21:02,328 --> 00:21:03,429
-Thank you.
