00:22:50,903 --> 00:22:54,139
I'm jealous you got to have this
since you were a kid.

455
00:22:54,306 --> 00:22:56,642
You also made memories with your parents.

456
00:22:57,142 --> 00:22:59,411
-I want to have it until the day I die.
