00:22:59,545 --> 00:23:02,948
You would be so sad
if this restaurant were to shut down.

458
00:23:03,549 --> 00:23:04,683
Yes.

459
00:23:04,817 --> 00:23:08,120
I like going to unfamiliar places,

460
00:23:08,187 --> 00:23:09,521
going to unfamiliar restaurants

