462
00:23:11,323 --> 00:23:14,793
-Someday, we should go on a drive…
-Yes.

463
00:23:14,927 --> 00:23:18,631
…to an unfamiliar place
and find good restaurants.

464
00:23:18,764 --> 00:23:20,165
-That sounds nice.
-Yes.

465
00:23:20,266 --> 00:23:23,168
We would wander around
looking for good food.

466
00:23:23,269 --> 00:23:26,438
You're already coming up
with a new program idea.

467
00:23:26,505 --> 00:23:28,340
